    {
      "id": "edge-required",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Required Structure",
      "position": {
        "x": -420,
        "y": 200
      },
      "width": 420,
      "height": 320,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Required Structure\n\nEvery persisted edge MUST include:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"id\": \"string\",\n  \"source\": \"node-id\",\n  \"target\": \"node-id\",\n  \"sourcePort\": \"handle-or-port-id\",\n  \"targetPort\": \"handle-or-port-id\"\n}\n```\n\n- `id` must be unique within the graph\n- readable stable ids are valid; UUIDs are allowed but not required\n- `source` and `target` must reference existing nodes\n- `sourcePort` and `targetPort` are the stored semantic endpoints\n- the canonical default endpoint is explicit `root`\n- if `type` is omitted, the renderer still resolves the edge using plain defaults",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "identity": {
