    {
      "id": "edge-agent-rules",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Agent Rules",
      "position": {
        "x": 1190,
        "y": 560
      },
      "width": 420,
      "height": 250,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Agent Rules (REQUIRED)\n\nAgents MUST:\n- read edge + port contracts\n- refuse incompatible edges\n- write explicit endpoint ids, including explicit `root` when using the default endpoint\n- prefer add/remove over rewire unless the task explicitly calls for retargeting an existing edge\n- emit errors, never guess\n- preserve edge identity only when the user or workflow clearly intends a true edge update",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "identity": {
            "graphId": "markdown_class",
            "name": "markdown Node Class",
            "version": "0.1.0",
            "description": "Canonical markdown content node.",
